main event: Two unidentified objects were seen flying in a westerly direction over Lakeport, California on July 22, 1956.
interesting points: The objects were observed visually by the witness for 3-4 seconds.
The objects were described as luminous and moving at an estimated speed of 600 miles per hour.
The objects disappeared from sight gradually.
The weather at the time was clear.
The observer was convinced the objects were genuine unidentified flying objects.
